Play custom sounds with key binds / mutate commands!

- Anti-Spam features (Delay, Timeout)
- Easy configuration
- Easy to use (Best way is to bind keys with your most likable sounds)
- 17x Base Sounds (Can increase without the need of editing code)
- Fun ? ;p

[h1][b][u]Notes[/u][/b][/h1]

- Mut is [b]WHITELISTED[/b] on dedicated servers

[h1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/h1]

- 4

[h1][b][u]Sample Config[/u][/b][/h1]

[code]
[KFSoundBoard.KFSoundBoard]
bDebug=True
# If True, every time a sound is used it will be displayed as a server message in the chat like this
# e.g. Meow! (Vel-San)
bNotifyOnSoundUsed=True
# Delay between 2 consecutive sounds (to avoid spam)
# Recommended 5 in case a souns lasts longer than 5 seconds :)
iDelay=5
# Number of times a player can use sounds consecutively, before they get timedout
# To bypass the timeout, simply let another played use play a sound :)
# This is intended to avoid players always hijacking the sounds and not letting others
# play anything
iTimeOut=3
# Command that will activate a sound
# Usage: mutate do meow
# meow is case insensitive, so you can do meow or MeOw etc..
sPlaySoundCMD=do
# List that holds all custom sounds
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.Animals.Meow",SoundTag="Cat",SoundBind="Meow")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.Animals.Bark",SoundTag="Dog",SoundBind="Woof")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.Human.Sneeze",SoundTag="Baby",SoundBind="Sneeze")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.Human.Kiss",SoundTag="Baby",SoundBind="Kiss")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.Joki_Laugh",SoundTag="Loki-Laugh",SoundBind="Laugh")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.AhPuch_NanuNanu",SoundTag="AhPuch-Nanu",SoundBind="Nanu")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.Aphro_Laugh",SoundTag="Aphro-Laugh",SoundBind="Laugh2")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.ArchonThanatos_FearNothing",SoundTag="Thana-Fear",SoundBind="FearNothing")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.HalloweenAwilix_MissMe",SoundTag="Awilix-MissMe",SoundBind="MissMe")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.KawaiiBastet_Senpai",SoundTag="Bastet-Senpai",SoundBind="Senpai")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.KingBacchus_Freakout",SoundTag="Bacchus-Freak",SoundBind="Freakout")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.KingBacchus_Silly",SoundTag="Bacchus-Silly",SoundBind="Silly")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.LunarTango_Ayayay",SoundTag="Change-Ayayay",SoundBind="Ayayay")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.OperaBacchus_CryForMe",SoundTag="Bacchus-CryForMe",SoundBind="CryForMe")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.RagnarokFenrir_Pathetic",SoundTag="Fenrir-Pathetic",SoundBind="Pathetic")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.RagnarokFenrir_Silence",SoundTag="Fenrir-Silence",SoundBind="Silence")
SoundList=(Sound="SoundBoardSND.SMITE.Thanatos_Laugh",SoundTag="Thana-Laugh",SoundBind="Laugh3")
# Color Tags for messages | Do not change :)
ColorList=(ColorName="Red",ColorTag="%r",Color=(B=0,G=0,R=200,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Orange",ColorTag="%o",Color=(B=0,G=127,R=255,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Yellow",ColorTag="%y",Color=(B=0,G=255,R=255,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Green",ColorTag="%g",Color=(B=0,G=200,R=0,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Blue",ColorTag="%b",Color=(B=200,G=100,R=0,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Teal",ColorTag="%t",Color=(B=113,G=179,R=60,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="Violet",ColorTag="%v",Color=(B=139,G=0,R=255,A=0))
ColorList=(ColorName="White",ColorTag="%w",Color=(B=200,G=200,R=200,A=0))
[/code]

[h1][b][u]File Names[/u][/b][/h1]

- \System\KFSoundBoard.u
- \System\KFSoundBoard.ucl
- \System\SoundBoardConfig.ini

- \Sounds\SoundBoardSND.uax

[h1][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/h1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (Recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list

[i]How to add more sounds ?[/i]

- Open SoundBoardSND.uax with Killing Floor SDK
- Import the sound (.wav) you want under the SoundGroup you would like
- Save the .uax (Overwrite, it's fine)
- Add the new sound in the config!
- Profit!

[h1][b][u]Class Names[/u][/b][/h1]

- Mut: KFSoundBoard.KFSoundBoard

